Wigan Warriors beat St Helens 12-4 at the DW Stadium on Friday night . 
  Dom Manfredi scored the first try of the game for Wigan Warriors . 
  Louie McCarthy-Scarsbrook and Joe Burgess also crossed for the home side . 
  Saints lost the Grand-Final to Wigan in October . 
  Wigan climb to third in the First Utility Super League . 
 